{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I never heard about her experiences in the convent, although I do remember her once saying that it was not always the same convent.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were taken in the night, because there were searches in convents also from one to another to another.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she didn't wind up in the same convent as she was when she was first taken there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But she came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, at that time--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the same area, or the same neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't want to leave that neighborhood just in case my brothers and sister would come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where would they look?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where would they search?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't want to leave the community that they would know where we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We left names at those houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We left names in-- in certainly, the Barniche's were still alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And however terrible they may have been, I don't think they would have denied information to my brothers and sisters if they came back if they were able to tell them where we would be.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took on a place very near the area where we were hidden, in the same community.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was only near 11 at that point, and my sister was about 15 and 16.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had no family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had nobody left.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
